{"tid":607774,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[找數。真抽飛] 17/ 6 張敬軒 HinSIDEOUT 演唱會","createTime":"2018-03-27T14:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T01:24:06.000Z","uid":70708,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0e049f15e1bd3e6ac78619eed5ac41696ee4a596","tid":607774,"uid":70708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"事源於張敬軒 HINS (15) dklm黑洞閪位討論區，之前係依個post lm 嘅巴絲應該知係做咩嘅。<br />\n<br />\n條list 人數多, 我又OT 依家先整合比多少少時間我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10:45 開始抽<br />\n<br />\n一陣會抽, 抽中要符合以下條件先會比你地: <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我都係想同一班歌迷睇, 但唔係忽然歌迷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1) 貼上<br />\nlihkg 名+ HINS LIVE IN PASSION 票尾<br />\n或<br />\nlihkg 名+ 5隻軒仔嘅CD<br />\n<br />\n2) 中籤者,10分鐘內要到post 內出現<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0801b1cf768cd4f084ce2fddfad61a81d36703d0","tid":607774,"uid":70708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:33:10.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"175c6ac412b6cf807eb9873f468bfc81520ed388","tid":607774,"uid":34314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:38:35.000Z","msg":"post 內出現係呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3198f861cef8d30461592a32fd96d00010d930","tid":607774,"uid":79859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:41:03.000Z","msg":"無留過言<br />\n欣賞樓主呢種方法<br />\n有心巴打有好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167dd6930f875a39f2e504cc956d4437271075c6","tid":607774,"uid":5641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6893ad39c2e677d39a10cdae2193c48396a698e3","tid":607774,"uid":70708,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:44:45.000Z","msg":"出咗第一條list 先<br />\n整到攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會抽17/6 780 飛， 大家幫手推比啲巴絲睇啦<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n親親太陽<br />\nJD男神<br />\n内田真禮<br />\n殺羊少女<br />\n一二三。三二一<br />\npeterchiu1028<br />\nVirgil_VanDijk<br />\n君士坦丁堡<br />\n看不見？<br />\n膠刀肺豉脾<br />\n地盤の猛鳩<br />\n野豬騎士<br />\nCD*ROM<br />\njessconte<br />\n艾兜<br />\n我好凍<br />\nM.Icardi🔵🌚<br />\n印度數學佬(生番)<br />\n藍字黑絲<br />\n青春常駐<br />\nRainDeer<br />\n放低很多<br />\n聚集記憶的時間<br />\n廢青狼<br />\n喬正初<br />\n汝娘波遮汝<br />\n林鄭長官行政月娥<br />\nPoketchu💋<br />\n夏日葵<br />\n瑪黑絲煮意<br />\n緋荔榭&middot;少女<br />\n啊朗好波<br />\n爛賭架妹<br />\n有D危<br />\n蕃茄薯片<br />\n反轉再反轉<br />\n不牛動奶<br />\n鋼鐵烏魯魯<br />\n可愛的瘋子<br />\nAspirin<br />\n今晚11點你做乜鳩<br />\nSephiroth<br />\n花生冰<br />\n籮柚痕<br />\n屌你都晒鳩氣<br />\nAfterAllThisTime<br />\n失憶&middot;蝴蝶<br />\n將軍澳貓奴<br />\nKerororo<br />\n關心一線專員2<br />\n清水撚<br />\n月黑風高瘋戀一場<br />\n小刺蛋蛋<br />\n黑白配<br />\n天達獅子<br />\n病態三部曲<br />\n帶番個頭盔先<br />\n用美極沖涼<br />\n我眼中的那個你"},{"pid":"09d638454cb983dadd17fabffa836e617eea752b","tid":607774,"uid":70708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"睇黎找數失敗, 係唔係隔得太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448e0f4f66d87a316e9673c3bdeb18bee62c7ef2","tid":607774,"uid":5641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09d638454cb983dadd17fabffa836e617eea752b","tid":607774,"uid":70708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"睇黎找數失敗, 係唔係隔得太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:50:35.000Z","msg":"係依個post留左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b171f62f001cd8a094d1f4cf110860cd1a803238","tid":607774,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquo